data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLERS 
Welcome to 311 Falcon Way, a charming single-family home located in the heart of Wright City, Missouri. This picturesque property features a spacious layout with 4 bed, 3 bath, 3-car garage. The open living area is perfect for entertaining, with plenty of natural light. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting modern appliances, walk-in pantry and ample counter space. The master suite is a peaceful retreat, complete with a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms offer versatility for family and guests. The highlight of this home, the nearly finished basement, which features a large bedroom with a massive walk-in closet, full bathroom, living room, additional room ready for a full kitchen and lots of storage. Outside, the property offers a beautifully landscapes yard. The backyard is a private oasis, ideal for relaxing or hosting gatherings. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own and experience the beauty of Wright City living!
